'''馬克·安德魯·雷諾茲'''（{{lang-en|Mark Andrew Reynolds}}, {{bd|1983年|8月3日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的內野手，生涯曾效力過響尾蛇、金鶯、印地安人、洋基、釀酒人、紅雀、洛磯與國民等隊，現為自由球員。常打全壘打、高三振率及出色的防守能力為其打擊特色。

2004年大聯盟選秀，響尾蛇隊在第16輪選進雷諾茲。
==職業生涯==
===亞利桑那響尾蛇===
====2007年====
5月16日，因為陣中內野手Chad Tracy受傷，因此雷諾茲從2A直升大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://arizona.diamondbacks.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20070516&content_id=1968574&vkey=news_ari&fext=.jsp&c_id=ari|title=Notes: Reynolds makes first ML start|last=Gilbert|first=Steve|date=May 16, 2007|publisher=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|accessdate=January 7, 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110610120115/http://arizona.diamondbacks.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20070516&content_id=1968574&vkey=news_ari&fext=.jsp&c_id=ari|archive-date=2011-06-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>他在生涯前15場比賽就打進14分打點。

該年他打擊率2成79，17轟62分打點。不過他也吞下129次三振。

10月3日，國聯分區賽第一場，雷諾茲在第7局擊出超前比數的全壘打，最後響尾蛇3場橫掃小熊。

雷諾茲在國聯冠軍賽的第3場也擊出全壘打，不過球隊4場遭到洛磯隊橫掃出局。
====2008年====
9月25日，雷諾茲吞下單季第200次三振。打破2007年由[[萊恩·霍華德|萊恩·霍華德]]創下的單季199次三振紀錄。最後雷諾茲該季吞下204次三振，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20080925&content_id=3546636&vkey=news_ari&fext=.jsp&c_id=ari |title=Reynolds breaks strikeout record |accessdate=March 18, 2009 |last=Gilbert |first=Steve |date=September 25, 2008 |publisher=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]] |archive-date=2012-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104091311/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20080925&content_id=3546636&vkey=news_ari&fext=.jsp&c_id=ari |dead-url=no }}</ref>三振率高達33.3%。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/MLB/2008-ratio-batting.shtml |title=2008 Major League Baseball Batting Ratios |work=Baseball-Reference.com |date= |accessdate=December 10, 2012 |archive-date=2020-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200527095733/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/MLB/2008-ratio-batting.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

而他該年34次守備失誤與.907的守備率皆為三壘手最慘的數據。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/stats/fielding/_/year/2008/position/3b/order/false|title=MLB Player Fielding Stats – As 3b – 2008|publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|accessdate=January 7, 2010|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304134321/http://espn.go.com/mlb/stats/fielding/_/year/2008/position/3b/order/false|dead-url=no}}</ref>另外他該年打擊率為2成39，28轟97分打點。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://arizona.diamondbacks.mlb.com/team/player.jsp?player_id=448602|title=Mark Reynolds Stats, Video Highlights, Photos, Bio|website=Arizona Diamondbacks|publisher=MLB|date=|accessdate=December 10, 2012|archive-date=2010-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100619195044/http://arizona.diamondbacks.mlb.com/team/player.jsp?player_id=448602|dead-url=no}}</ref>
====2009年====
該年明星賽，雷諾茲入選最終決選名單。不過他票選輸給[[謝恩·維克托里諾|謝恩·維克托里諾]]和[[巴勃羅·桑多瓦爾|巴勃羅·桑多瓦爾]]，無緣入選明星賽。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090709&content_id=5787776&vkey=allstar2009&fext=.jsp |title='Bran-Torino' takes a ride to All-Star Game |last=Newman |first=Mark |date=July 9, 2009 |publisher=[[MLB|MLB]] |accessdate=January 7, 2010 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116130424/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090709&content_id=5787776&vkey=allstar2009&fext=.jsp |dead-url=no }}</ref>

7月28日，他在[[大通體育場|大通體育場]]擊出481英尺的全壘打。這支全壘打是2009年最遠的全壘打。該年他擊出44轟，其中有25轟的飛行距離都超過400英尺。

8月10日，他在那週的打擊率高達4成48，擊出6轟10分打點。他也擊敗隊友Ryan Roberts拿下單週最佳球員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://arizona.diamondbacks.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090810&content_id=6352644&vkey=news_ari&fext=.jsp&c_id=ari|title=Reynolds named NL Player of the Week|website=Arizona Diamondbacks|publisher=MLB|date=|accessdate=December 10, 2012|archive-date=2011-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110610120237/http://arizona.diamondbacks.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090810&content_id=6352644&vkey=news_ari&fext=.jsp&c_id=ari|dead-url=no}}</ref>

該年他打擊率為2成60，44轟102分打點。另還有98得分與24次盜壘成功。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/stats/batting/_/seasontype/2/sort/strikeouts/order/true |title=MLB Player Batting Stats – 2009 |publisher=ESPN |date= |accessdate=December 10, 2012 |archive-date=2016-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410160533/http://espn.go.com/mlb/stats/batting/_/seasontype/2/sort/strikeouts/order/true |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過他單季吞下223次三振成為生涯新高。
====2010年====
3月18日，他與球隊簽下3年1450萬美元的合約。<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://arizona.diamondbacks.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20100318&content_id=8830846&vkey=pr_ari&fext=.jsp&c_id=ari|title=Reynolds signs multiyear contract with D-backs|date=March 18, 2010|website=Arizona Diamondbacks|publisher=MLB|accessdate=December 10, 2012|archive-date=2012-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120406195654/http://arizona.diamondbacks.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20100318&content_id=8830846&vkey=pr_ari&fext=.jsp&c_id=ari|dead-url=no}}</ref>5月20日，他面對巨人隊擊出生涯第100轟。該年他打擊率僅1成98，卻擊出32轟85分打點。單季83次保送也是生涯新高。

雷諾茲也成為了史上首位打擊率乘以1000還比生涯三振數還少的野手。<ref>{{cite web |author='Duk |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/blog/big_league_stew/post/More-K-than-BA-Mark-Reynolds-in-position-to-sta?urn=mlb-273913 |title=More K than BA: Mark Reynolds in position to start exclusive club |date=October 1, 2010 |work=Yahoo! Sports |accessdate=December 10, 2012 |archive-date=2016-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410100851/http://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/blog/big_league_stew/post/More-K-than-BA-Mark-Reynolds-in-position-to-sta?urn=mlb-273913 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===巴爾的摩金鶯===
2010年12月6日，響尾蛇將雷諾茲與一名日後指定球員(John Hester)交易至金鶯隊，換來David Hernandez和Kam Mickolio。<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://baltimore.orioles.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20101206&content_id=16263224&vkey=pr_bal&fext=.jsp&c_id=bal |title=Orioles acquire 3B Mark Reynolds from Arizona Diamondbacks |date=December 6, 2010 |website=Baltimore Orioles |publisher=MLB |accessdate=December 10, 2012 |archive-date=2012-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120406212527/http://baltimore.orioles.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20101206&content_id=16263224&vkey=pr_bal&fext=.jsp&c_id=bal |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release|url=http://baltimore.orioles.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20110430&content_id=18448540&vkey=pr_bal&fext=.jsp&c_id=bal|title=Orioles receive CA John Hester from Arizona|date=April 30, 2011|website=Baltimore Orioles|publisher=MLB|accessdate=December 10, 2012|archive-date=2011-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110506172525/http://baltimore.orioles.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20110430&content_id=18448540&vkey=pr_bal&fext=.jsp&c_id=bal|dead-url=no}}</ref>
====2011年====
該年他單季發生31次守備失誤為大聯盟最多，8成97的守備率也是三壘手最低。而他單季也吞下196次三振，為美聯最多。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/MLB/2011-fielding-leaders.shtml |title=2011 Major League Baseball Fielding Leaders |work=Baseball-Reference.com |date= |accessdate=December 10, 2012 |archive-date=2011-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111113162818/http://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/MLB/2011-fielding-leaders.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="baseball-reference.com">{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/r/reynoma01.shtml |title=Mark Reynolds Statistics and History |publisher=Baseball-Reference.com |date= |accessdate=December 10, 2012 |archive-date=2009-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090405094215/http://www.baseball-reference.com/players/r/reynoma01.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/stats/fielding/_/seasontype/2/position/3b |title=2012 Regular Season MLB Baseball 3B Fielding Statistics – Major League Baseball |publisher=ESPN |date= |accessdate=December 10, 2012 |archive-date=2016-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410183326/http://espn.go.com/mlb/stats/fielding/_/seasontype/2/position/3b |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過他單季37轟名列美聯第4。

8月7日，他成為史上第一位在[[金鶯公園|金鶯公園]]將球打上外野第二層看台的球員。這支全壘打的飛行距離經過推算長達463英尺。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hittrackeronline.com/index.php?h=BAL&p=TOR&b=Oriole%2BPark%2Bat%2BCamden%2BYards |title=2011 ESPN Home Run Tracker |work= |date= |accessdate=June 7, 2017}}</ref>
====2012年====
5月29日，他僅花了747場比賽就達成生涯被三振1000次的尷尬紀錄，成為史上最快達成此紀錄的球員。

該年球季，雷諾茲被安排在一壘守備，三壘則由[[克里斯·戴維斯|克里斯·戴維斯]]來守備。雷諾茲以一壘手身分出賽108場，僅發生5次失誤。9成95的守備率讓他排名大聯盟第4。

8月17日，老虎隊的Jhonny Peralta擊出三壘滾地球，三壘手[[曼尼·馬查多|曼尼·馬查多]]在把球丟向一壘的時候，雷諾茲為了接球讓腳離開壘包，最終一壘審判決Peralta擊出安打上壘。雷諾茲因為在和一壘審爭論時將手套摔向地上而遭驅逐出場。後來總教練[[巴克·休瓦特|巴克·休瓦特]]認為雷諾茲不應該被驅逐，雖然最後休瓦特也被驅逐出場，不過主審反而讓雷諾茲重回賽場上。

9月6日，他面對洋基隊時擊出雙響砲。他成為1918年後第二位單季3次面對洋基隊擊出雙響砲的球員。<ref>{{cite web |author=ALDS – GAME 5 Game 5Fri, Oct 12 |url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/player/_/id/28772/mark-reynolds |title=Mark Reynolds Stats, News, Pictures, Bio, Videos – Baltimore Orioles |publisher=ESPN |date=May 16, 2007 |accessdate=December 10, 2012 |archive-date=2016-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160729161456/http://espn.go.com/mlb/player/_/id/28772/mark-reynolds |dead-url=no }}</ref>

該年他打擊率2成21，23轟69分打點。球季結束後，金鶯沒有和雷諾茲續約。於是他成為自由球員。
===克里夫蘭印地安人===
2012年12月9日，雷諾茲與印地安人隊簽下1年的合約。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20121209&content_id=40590906&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb|title=Reynolds agrees to one-year deal with Indians|last1=Ghiroli|first1=Brittany|last2=Bastain|first2=Jordan|work=MLB.com|date=December 9, 2012|accessdate=December 9, 2012|archive-date=2013-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231223514/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20121209&content_id=40590906&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年4月13日，他面對白襪隊的[[克里斯·塞爾|克里斯·塞爾]]擊出滿貫砲。他在4月的打擊率高達3成01，不過到了5月卻只剩下1成87。8月8日，他被球隊給指定轉讓。<ref>{{cite news |agency=Associated Press |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/indians/2013/08/08/indians-designate-mark-reynolds/2632269/ |title=Indians designate slugger Mark Reynolds |work=USA Today |date=August 8, 2013 |accessdate=August 17, 2013 |archive-date=2018-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180626171224/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/indians/2013/08/08/indians-designate-mark-reynolds/2632269/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>8月12日，他遭到球隊釋出。他在印地安人擊出15轟，打擊率卻只有2成15。
===紐約洋基===
2013年8月13日，雷諾茲加入洋基隊，<ref>{{cite web |last=Heyman |first=John |url=http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/writer/jon-heyman/23167298/sources-mark-reynolds-has-deal-with-yankees/23167298/sources-mark-reynolds-has-deal-with-yankees |title=Yankees land power bat with addition of Mark Reynolds |publisher=Cbssports.com |date= |accessdate=August 17, 2013 |archive-date=2016-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412195700/http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/writer/jon-heyman/23167298/sources-mark-reynolds-has-deal-with-yankees/23167298/sources-mark-reynolds-has-deal-with-yankees |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130815&content_id=57132070&vkey=news_nyy&c_id=nyy |title=Slugger Mark Reynolds reaches deal with Yankees |publisher=MLB.com |date=August 15, 2013 |accessdate=August 17, 2013 |archive-date=2014-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140409073932/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130815&content_id=57132070&vkey=news_nyy&c_id=nyy |dead-url=no }}</ref>他身穿條紋衣的首個打席就擊出全壘打。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/yankees/yankees-insider-reynolds-hits-mark-debut-article-1.1429510 |title=Mark Reynolds homers in Yankees debut against Red Sox |work=New York Daily News |first1=Mark |last1=Feinsand |first2=Roger |last2=Rubin |date=August 17, 2013 |accessdate=September 8, 2013 |archive-date=2018-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180626221953/http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/yankees/yankees-insider-reynolds-hits-mark-debut-article-1.1429510 |dead-url=no }}</ref>8月28日，因為[[羅賓森·坎諾|羅賓森·坎諾]]和[[愛德華多·努涅斯|愛德華多·努涅斯]]都進入傷兵名單，所以雷諾茲首次進入洋基隊的先發名單中。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hardballtalk.nbcsports.com/2013/08/28/mark-reynolds-is-the-yankees-starting-second-baseman-tonight/ |title=Mark Reynolds is the Yankees starting second baseman tonight – HardballTalk<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2019-08-23 |archive-date=2014-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140918050740/http://hardballtalk.nbcsports.com/2013/08/28/mark-reynolds-is-the-yankees-starting-second-baseman-tonight/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>該年他在洋基隊出賽36場，打擊率2成36，6轟19分打點。
===密爾瓦基釀酒人===
2014年1月17日，他以小聯盟合約加入釀酒人。他在釀酒人隊出賽130場，擊出22轟45分打點，打擊率卻僅有1成96。
===聖路易紅雀隊===
2014年12月11日，他以一年200萬美元的合約加入紅雀隊。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2014/12/cardinals-to-sign-mark-reynolds.html |title=Cardinals sign Mark Reynolds |first=Jeff |last=Todd |work=mlb traderumors.com |date=December 11, 2014 |access-date=2019-08-23 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112005931/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2014/12/cardinals-to-sign-mark-reynolds.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>由於他連續5個球季打擊率都不到2成3，因此他在紅雀隊主要擔任一壘手[[麥特·亞當斯|麥特·亞當斯]]和三壘手[[麥特·卡本特_(棒球選手)|麥特·卡本特]]的替補。<ref>{{cite web |last=Goold |first=Derrick |url=http://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cards-sign-reynolds-could-platoon-with-adams/article_9f1d15de-e47e-51f7-810b-af5d39607d83.html |title=Cards sign Reynolds, could platoon with Adams |work=[[St._Louis_Post-Dispatch|St. Louis Post-Dispatch]] |date=December 12, 2014 |accessdate=December 13, 2014 |archive-date=2018-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180708062609/https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cards-sign-reynolds-could-platoon-with-adams/article_9f1d15de-e47e-51f7-810b-af5d39607d83.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

7月12日，雷諾茲首度達成他在紅雀隊的雙響砲紀錄。這也是他生涯第22次達成單場雙響。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Berry |first1=Adam |last2=McGonigal |first2=John |url=http://m.cardinals.mlb.com/news/article/136151580/andrew-mccutchen-hits-walk-off-homer-for-bucs |title=Cards drop marathon heartbreaker to Bucs |website=St. Louis Cardinals |publisher=MLB |date=July 12, 2015 |accessdate=July 12, 2015 |archive-date=2015-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150910191858/http://m.cardinals.mlb.com/news/article/136151580/andrew-mccutchen-hits-walk-off-homer-for-bucs |dead-url=no }}</ref>該年他出賽140場，打擊率2成30，13轟48分打點。
===科羅拉多洛磯===
2015年12月16日，他和洛磯隊簽下1年2600萬美元的合約，另外還有1100萬美元的激勵獎金。<ref>{{cite news |agency=Associated Press |url=http://gazette.com/rockies-and-reynolds-finalize-1-year-2.6-million-deal/article/1565854 |title=Rockies and Reynolds finalize 1-year, $2.6 million deal |work=[[The_Gazette_(Colorado_Springs)|The Gazette]] |location=Colorado Springs, Colorado |date=December 16, 2015 |accessdate=December 16, 2015 |archive-date=2018-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180626164012/http://gazette.com/rockies-and-reynolds-finalize-1-year-2.6-million-deal/article/1565854 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2016年他出賽118場，打擊率2成82，14轟53分打點。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/r/reynoma01.shtml|title=Mark Reynolds Statistics and History|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|accessdate=February 1, 2017|archive-date=2009-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090405094215/http://www.baseball-reference.com/players/r/reynoma01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年2月1日，他與球隊簽下小聯盟合約，並受邀參加春訓。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2017/02/rockies-to-re-sign-mark-reynolds.html|title=Rockies Re-Sign Mark Reynolds|last=Todd|first=Jeff|work=mlbtraderumors.com|date=February 1, 2017|accessdate=February 1, 2017|archive-date=2019-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190521212144/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2017/02/rockies-to-re-sign-mark-reynolds.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

由於[[伊恩·德斯蒙德|伊恩·德斯蒙德]]受傷，因此雷諾茲成為2017年洛磯隊開季先發一壘手。5月9日，他達成連續4場開轟的個人紀錄。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Harding |first1=Thomas |last2=Perkins |first2=Owen |url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/229239780/rockies-beat-cubs-in-game-1-of-doubleheader/?game_pk=490574 |title=Rox ride 6-run 3rd to breezy G1 win over Cubs |work=MLB.com |date=May 9, 2017 |accessdate=May 9, 2017}}</ref>該年他打擊率2成67，30轟97分打點，還有175次被三振。<ref name=castillo20180412>{{Cite web |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/nationals-journal/wp/2018/04/12/nationals-agree-to-minor-league-deal-with-veteran-slugger-mark-reynolds/ |title=Castillo, Jorge, "Nationals agree to minor league deal with veteran slugger Mark Reynolds," washingtonpost.com, April 12, 2018, 8:41 p.m. EDT. |access-date=2019-08-23 |archive-date=2018-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180616154122/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/nationals-journal/wp/2018/04/12/nationals-agree-to-minor-league-deal-with-veteran-slugger-mark-reynolds/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===華盛頓國民===
2017年球季結束，雷諾茲成為自由球員。2018年4月12日，他與國民隊簽下小聯盟合約。他在3A出賽10場，打擊率2成31。<ref name=reddington20180512>{{Cite web |url=https://www.federalbaseball.com/2018/5/12/17348062/washington-nationals-place-ryan-zimmerman-on-10-day-dl-bring-mark-reynolds-up-triple-a-syracuse |title=Reddington, Patrick, "Washington Nationals place Ryan Zimmerman on 10-Day DL; bring Mark Reynolds up from Triple-A," federalbaseball.com, May 12, 2018, 3;32 p.m. EDT. |access-date=2019-08-23 |archive-date=2020-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002143225/https://www.federalbaseball.com/2018/5/12/17348062/washington-nationals-place-ryan-zimmerman-on-10-day-dl-bring-mark-reynolds-up-triple-a-syracuse |dead-url=no }}</ref>後來因為一壘手[[萊恩·齊默爾曼|萊恩·齊默爾曼]]受傷，他在5月12日登上大聯盟。

5月13日為雷諾茲身穿國民球衣的第一場比賽，而他在那場比賽就擊出雙響砲。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/nationals/mark-reynoldss-two-hrs-in-nationals-debut-power-win-over-diamondbacks/2018/05/13/33d834cc-571b-11e8-b656-a5f8c2a9295d_story.html|title=Mark Reynolds’s two HRs in Nationals debut power win over Diamondbacks|last=Janes|first=Chelsea|work=washingtonpost.com|date=May 13, 2018|accessdate=May 14, 2018|archive-date=2018-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181128183317/https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/nationals/mark-reynoldss-two-hrs-in-nationals-debut-power-win-over-diamondbacks/2018/05/13/33d834cc-571b-11e8-b656-a5f8c2a9295d_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>7月7日，他締造單場10分打點。追平2017年由Scooter Gennett創下的單場打點紀錄。7月9日，他再度獲選為單週最佳球員。該年他打擊率為2成48，13轟40分打點。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/r/reynoma01.shtml |title=Mark Reynolds Stats {{!}} Baseball-Reference.com<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2019-08-23 |archive-date=2009-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090405094215/http://www.baseball-reference.com/players/r/reynoma01.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===重回洛磯隊===
2019年1月30日，他再度與洛磯隊簽下小聯盟合約。<ref name="MLB13019">[https://www.mlb.com/news/mark-reynolds-signs-minors-deal-with-rockies/c-303361456 Reynolds returning to Rox on Minors deal] {{Wayback|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/mark-reynolds-signs-minors-deal-with-rockies/c-303361456 |date=20190205183249 }} (MLB.com)</ref>最後他與球隊簽下1年100萬美元加上100萬激勵獎金的合約，<ref>[http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/25888612/mark-reynolds-reaches-minor-league-deal-colorado-rockies Mark Reynolds reaches minor league deal with Colorado Rockies] {{Wayback|url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/25888612/mark-reynolds-reaches-minor-league-deal-colorado-rockies |date=20200924115702 }} (AP)</ref>做為[[丹尼爾·墨菲|丹尼爾·墨菲]]的替補。他在2019年7月21日遭到球隊指定轉讓，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.denverpost.com/2019/07/21/veteran-slugger-mark-reynolds-designated-for-assignment-by-rockies/|title=Veteran slugger Mark Reynolds designated for assignment by Rockies|author=Patrick Saunders|newspaper=[[The_Denver_Post|The Denver Post]]|date=July 21, 2019|accessdate=July 21, 2019|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127071420/https://www.denverpost.com/2019/07/21/veteran-slugger-mark-reynolds-designated-for-assignment-by-rockies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>7月26日遭到釋出。
